content.description:
This is a traverse that uses the start from

Cruelty Free

. Reach up to a huge side pull for the left, then find one for the right. Move right to a huge rail, then move around the bulge. There are more crimps waiting on the other side. Make a reach out to 2 finger pocket, and rock over to easier terrain. Finish out right to the peak of the formation.
content.protection: A pad. Watch out for stump and tree that are in the fall zone.
content.location:
It is to the right of

Farm Fresh

.

content.description: Start with your hands matched on a good shelf. Place your feet on a large, lower shelf. Move your right hand just a little up to the right, and find the undercling pinch. Stand high, and reach for the large crimp rail. Pull yourself up to a mantel, and you're done.
content.location: It is the furthest left problem on the east side of the block.

content.description: Start matched on a small jug. Reach up in into the crack. You'll find some good constriction spots in the crack to pull yourself up. There are lots of nobs up top to finish out on.
content.protection: A pad. Watch for a stump that is slightly too the right of the fall area.
content.location:
It is to the right of

Farm Fresh

.
